The paper discusses the generalization performance of overparameterized convolutional neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and explores the interplay between weight clustering and feature exploration at initialization, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
